query: DELETE a FROM historicoTextos a JOIN historicoTextos b ON a.tipo = b.tipo AND b.texto LIKE CONCAT(a.texto, '%') AND a.id != b.id AND LENGTH(a.texto) < LENGTH(b.texto);
